{"root":{"children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":2,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Ever faced challenges when trying to align elements on a webpage? You‚Äôre not alone. It‚Äôs a common hurdle for many developers. But there‚Äôs a solution: Flexbox. Born from the CSS3 specification, Flexbox offers a more efficient and straightforward way to design layouts.","type":"extended-text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1},{"type":"horizontalrule","version":1},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Why Flexbox?","type":"extended-text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"extended-heading","version":1,"tag":"h3"},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Flexbox simplifies web design. It allows you to organize, align, and distribute space among items in a container, even if their sizes are dynamic or unknown. It‚Äôs an essential tool that makes creating responsive and cohesive designs easier.","type":"extended-text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Kickstarting with Flexbox","type":"extended-text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"extended-heading","version":1,"tag":"h3"},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"To harness the power of Flexbox, set an element‚Äôs ","type":"extended-text","version":1},{"detail":0,"format":16,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"display","type":"extended-text","version":1},{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":" property to ","type":"extended-text","version":1},{"detail":0,"format":16,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"flex","type":"extended-text","version":1},{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":".","type":"extended-text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":